MT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-25/ty-article/.premium/police-chief-discourse-on-israel-police-has-crossed-a-red-line-police-are-not-a-militia/00000190-4e9c-d8cb-a19d-4fdff4e10000</guid></item><item><title>以色列最高法院规定国家必须征召极端正统派加入以色列国防军，这对内塔尼亚胡政府构成打击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-25/ty-article/.premium/in-blow-to-netanyahu-israels-top-court-says-state-must-draft-ultra-orthodox-to-army/0000018f-ed56-dc46-a5bf-fdd604e60000</link><description>经过多年的法律和政治争论，九名高等法​​院法官一致做出这一裁决，这将对内塔尼亚胡的执政联盟产生冲击波</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 08:05:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-25/ty-article/.premium/in-blow-to-netanyahu-israels-top-court-says-state-must-draft-ultra-orthodox-to-army/0000018f-ed56-dc46-a5bf-fdd604e60000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡主义已经失败，现在正危及以色列的安全</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-25/ty-article/.premium/the-netanyahu-doctrine-has-failed-and-now-it-is-endangering-israels-security/00000190-4bdc-d8cb-a19d-4bdf46290000</link><description>一个误判就可能导致以色列和真主党陷入全面战争，造成大量平民伤亡。尽管美国发誓支持以色列，但它坚称不能保证从耶路撒冷的角度来看最佳结果</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 03:00:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-25/ty-article/.premium/the-netanyahu-doctrine-has-failed-and-now-it-is-endangering-israels-security/00000190-4bdc-d8cb-a19d-4bdf46290000</guid></item><item><title>加沙报道：以色列国防军袭击加沙城至少13人死亡，其中包括哈马斯酋长哈尼亚的妹妹</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-25/ty-article-live/blinken-stresses-need-for-post-war-gaza-plan-in-meeting-with-gallant/00000190-4d36-d768-adf8-4db68ad70000</link><description>报告：美国官员警告真主党不要认为自己能够阻止以色列袭击黎巴嫩 ■ 以色列国防军宣布，被绑架的以色列士兵于 10 月 7 日被杀，他的尸体被关押在加沙 ■ 内塔尼亚胡：“致力于拜登概述的以色列提议” ■ 以色列国防军杀死哈马斯弹药生产工作的关键人物 ■ 美国军方负责人表示，美国可能无法像对付伊朗那样保护以色列免受真主党的袭击</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 02:46:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-25/ty-article-live/blinken-stresses-need-for-post-war-gaza-plan-in-meeting-with-gallant/00000190-4d36-d768-adf8-4db68ad70000</guid></item><item><title>解释：以色列的“潜艇事件”是什么？它会击沉内塔尼亚胡吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-25/ty-article/.premium/explained-what-is-israels-submarine-affair-and-could-it-sink-netanyahu/00000190-4c33-d8cb-a19d-4d73eee40000</link><description>国家调查委员会周一对所谓潜艇事件发出的警告信意味着什么？这些警告信是否会导致刑事调查？</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 21:56:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-25/ty-article/.premium/explained-what-is-israels-submarine-affair-and-could-it-sink-netanyahu/00000190-4c33-d8cb-a19d-4d73eee40000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡的潜艇警告信是以色列最大笨蛋的又一失败篇章</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-25/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-warning-letter-is-another-chapter-of-failure-for-israels-biggest-bungler/00000190-4bdc-d429-abfc-7bdee3520000</link><description>针对首相发出的警告信准确地描述了 10 月 7 日失败的序幕 - 以及从那一刻起随之而来的失败</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 21:28:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-25/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-warning-letter-is-another-chapter-of-failure-for-israels-biggest-bungler/00000190-4bdc-d429-abfc-7bdee3520000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军宣布被绑架的以色列士兵于10月7日被杀，其尸体被扣押在加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-24/ty-article/idf-announces-that-abducted-israeli-soldier-was-killed-on-oct-7-his-body-held-in-gaza/00000190-4b77-da60-a5b7-cfffb6b70000</link><description>中士。穆罕默德·阿特拉什少校是一名以色列国防军退伍军人，也是以色列国防军加沙分部的一名追踪员</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 20:45:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-24/ty-article/idf-announces-that-abducted-israeli-soldier-was-killed-on-oct-7-his-body-held-in-gaza/00000190-4b77-da60-a5b7-cfffb6b70000</guid></item><item><title>以色列儿童读物鼓励犹太人在黎巴嫩南部定居</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-06-24/ty-article/.premium/messianic-israelis-new-way-of-encouraging-settlement-in-south-lebanon-a-childrens-book/00000190-4ab3-da42-a1ba-7ffbefa00000</link><description>另外，7 月份参加耶路撒冷电影节的以色列电影、三位以色列摄影师反思了他们 10 月 7 日之后的作品以及歌手 Netta Barzilai 的新艺术方向</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 19:45:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-06-24/ty-article/.premium/messianic-israelis-new-way-of-encouraging-settlement-in-south-lebanon-a-childrens-book/00000190-4ab3-da42-a1ba-7ffbefa00000</guid></item><item><title>以色列向美国澄清，内塔尼亚胡的电视讲话并不反映加沙谈判立场的变化</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-24/ty-article/.premium/israel-tells-u-s-that-netanyahus-tv-remarks-dont-reflect-change-in-gaza-talks-stance/00000190-4b59-dafc-adb4-7bd9bffd0000</link><description>总理重申了之前的立场，并在议会讲话中澄清，他的政府“致力于拜登总统概述的以色列提案”</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 19:30:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-24/ty-article/.premium/israel-tells-u-s-that-netanyahus-tv-remarks-dont-reflect-change-in-gaza-talks-stance/00000190-4b59-dafc-adb4-7bd9bffd0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列即将与黎巴嫩真主党开战吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-24/ty-article/.premium/will-there-be-a-third-lebanon-war-maybe-not-as-soon-as-you-think-or-sooner/00000190-4b14-d91c-abba-ef14ba030000</link><description>随着以色列国防军缩小加沙的战斗规模，以色列的注意力越来越集中在北部边境和真主党的威胁上。全面战争可能还会发生，但双方目前也可能更愿意缓和局势</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 17:09:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-24/ty-article/.premium/will-there-be-a-third-lebanon-war-maybe-not-as-soon-as-you-think-or-sooner/00000190-4b14-d91c-abba-ef14ba030000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡的一位盟友被任命为以色列新闻频道的负责人。它的记者不会不战而屈人之兵</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-24/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-journalists-fighting-the-selection-of-a-netanyahu-stooge-to-head-israeli-news-channel/00000190-49d7-d8cb-a19d-49d749d10000</link><description>任命尤利娅·沙马洛夫·贝尔科维奇为以色列第 13 频道负责人被视为内塔尼亚胡及其支持者将新闻媒体转变为右翼回声室的最新尝试。妇女团体对她过去有关性骚扰的言论感到震惊，已与记者一起努力推翻这一举措</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 17:00:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-24/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-journalists-fighting-the-selection-of-a-netanyahu-stooge-to-head-israeli-news-channel/00000190-49d7-d8cb-a19d-49d749d10000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战事第 262 天：哈马斯与法塔赫和解谈判无限期推迟</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-24/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-262-hamas-fatah-reconciliation-talks-postponed-indefinitely/00000190-4b22-d768-adf8-4fb279770001</link><description>总理内塔尼亚胡表示，他仍然致力于拜登上个月提出的停火协议提案，此前他因表示支持与哈马斯的“部分”协议而遭到强烈反对。 人质和失踪家庭论坛发布了以色列人赫什·戈德堡-波林被绑架的画面。利维和埃利亚·科恩 ■ 以色列国防军称，他们在加沙打死了一名哈马斯高级官员 ■ 战争开始 262 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 16:51:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-24/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-262-hamas-fatah-reconciliation-talks-postponed-indefinitely/00000190-4b22-d768-adf8-4fb279770001</guid></item><item><title>家人播放了 10 月 7 日绑架的新镜头，其中包括以色列裔美国人赫什·戈德堡-波林 (Hersh Goldberg-Polin)</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-24/ty-article/families-air-footage-of-oct-7-abductions-including-of-hersh-goldberg-polin/00000190-4a70-dafc-adb4-7bf91f040000</link><description>这段视频长约两分钟，是用恐怖分子随身携带的摄像机拍摄的。 ■ 人质家属将这段视频标记为 262 天“忽视”的证据，敦促达成协议释放人质。 ■ Hersh Goldberg-Polin、Or Levy、Elia Cohen和阿隆·奥赫尔 (Alon Ohel) 在参加新星节派对后在加沙边境附近被绑架</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 15:59:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-24/ty-article/families-air-footage-of-oct-7-abductions-including-of-hersh-goldberg-polin/00000190-4a70-dafc-adb4-7bf91f040000</guid></item><item><title>联合国表示加沙的社会崩溃和犯罪限制了援助的分配，危及工人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-24/ty-article/.premium/un-says-social-breakdown-and-crime-in-gaza-limits-aid-distribution-endangers-workers/00000190-4a5e-d91c-abba-ef5e95450000</link><description>联合国的一份报告称，除了战斗，犯罪活动实际上阻碍了人道主义援助进入加沙的关键地点，并警告说“加沙南部可能很快就会出现与北部相同的灾难性饥饿水平”</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 15:40:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-24/ty-article/.premium/un-says-social-breakdown-and-crime-in-gaza-limits-aid-distribution-endangers-workers/00000190-4a5e-d91c-abba-ef5e95450000</guid></item><item><title>在与真主党的战争中，美国应该与内塔尼亚胡领导的以色列站在一起吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-24/ty-article-opinion/.premium/should-america-stand-with-netanyahus-israel-in-a-war-with-hezbollah/00000190-4a85-da60-a5b7-cfcf59160000</link><description>拜登面临一个难题：美国对以色列的大力支持赋予了内塔尼亚胡权力，内塔尼亚胡是一个精神病态的人权侵犯者，严重损害了美国的利益。即使战争爆发，是时候限制我们的支持了</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 15:29:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-24/ty-article-opinion/.premium/should-america-stand-with-netanyahus-israel-in-a-war-with-hezbollah/00000190-4a85-da60-a5b7-cfcf59160000</guid></item><item><title>民意调查：甘茨对内塔尼亚胡的领先优势稳步缩小；反对派集团仍占多数</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-24/ty-article/.premium/poll-gantz-lead-over-netanyahu-steadily-narrows-opposition-bloc-still-set-for-majority/00000190-4a6a-d429-abfc-7b7a32c40000</link><description>民意调查还预测，反对内塔尼亚胡的新右翼联盟可能赢得34个席位，成为以色列议会第一大党</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 14:17:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-24/ty-article/.premium/poll-gantz-lead-over-netanyahu-steadily-narrows-opposition-bloc-still-set-for-majority/00000190-4a6a-d429-abfc-7b7a32c40000</guid></item><item><title>人质家属告诉以色列立法者：部分协议就是彻底失败</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-24/ty-article/.premium/hostages-families-tell-israeli-lawmakers-partial-deal-is-total-failure/00000190-4ad1-da42-a1ba-7ffb53e40000</link><description>人质家属猛烈抨击内塔尼亚胡的言论，称他支持与哈马斯达成“部分协议”，根据该协议，只有部分人质可以回家。 “有一天内塔尼亚胡告诉我们达成了一项协议，另一天他又说了些什么。我怎样才能不发疯呢？人质的母亲说</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 14:07:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-24/ty-article/.premium/hostages-families-tell-israeli-lawmakers-partial-deal-is-total-failure/00000190-4ad1-da42-a1ba-7ffb53e40000</guid></item><item><title>以色列正处于法西斯主义的边缘。会跨过门槛吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-06-24/ty-article/.premium/israel-is-on-the-verge-of-fascism-will-it-cross-the-threshold/00000190-496a-d91c-abba-ef7aec290000</link><description>以色列正在经历一场小型内战，让人想起法西斯进军罗马前夕的魏玛-德国和意大利</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 13:41:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-06-24/ty-article/.premium/israel-is-on-the-verge-of-fascism-will-it-cross-the-threshold/00000190-496a-d91c-abba-ef7aec290000</guid></item></channel></rss>